thread.title: Government Bonds Notch Price Declines

author: wsjcom
title: Government Bonds Notch Price Declines

organizations.name: government bonds notch price declines investors

text:
Investors sold Treasurys on Friday as anxiety about an international trade war percolated global markets.
The yield on the 10-year Treasury note rose to 2.855%, from 2.802% on Thursday. Yields rise as bond prices fall.
